### TC-AMS-01 — AMS Findings Panel Displayed for Individual Farmer/Agent with Red Findings (Pre-Submit)

**Jira ID:** BISSAGL-X
**Priority:** High
**Type:** Functional
**Round:** Round 1
**Status:** Pre-Submit
**Labels:** AMS, FarmerDashboard, Round1, PreSubmit

**Test Data Required:**

- Individual herd with pending AMS Red findings (use SQL query 1 above)
- Agent login for that herd (use INET query above)

**Preconditions:**

- Herd has at least 1 Red AMS finding in Round 1
- Application is Pre-Submit (Not Started or Draft)
- Agent is logged in and viewing the Farmer Dashboard

**Test Steps:**

|Step|Action                                        |Expected Result                                                                              |
|----|----------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|1   |Log in as agent with valid credentials and OTP|Agent lands on BISS Home page                                                                |
|2   |Navigate to My Clients                        |My Clients page displayed                                                                    |
|3   |Search for herd with Red AMS findings         |Herd appears in results                                                                      |
|4   |Open Farmer Dashboard for herd                |Farmer Dashboard displayed                                                                   |
|5   |Locate the AMS Findings panel                 |Panel is visible on dashboard                                                                |
|6   |Verify panel header                           |Header reads **“AMS findings”**                                                              |
|7   |Verify AMS status section                     |AMS status is displayed underneath header                                                    |
|8   |Verify red triangle symbol                    |Red triangle (⚠) icon visible with label **“AMS findings”**                                  |
|9   |Verify Response Required label                |Label **“Response required”** displayed with red symbol to the right                         |
|10  |Verify count                                  |**“Amount”** label shown with the correct number of red notifications                        |
|11  |Verify Respond to findings button             |Green **“Respond to findings”** button is visible                                            |
|12  |Click Respond to findings button              |Navigates to AMS screen                                                                      |
|13  |Return to Farmer Dashboard                    |Navigate back to dashboard                                                                   |
|14  |Verify deadline message                       |Panel displays message: **“You have until 8 July 2026 to respond to your AMS notifications”**|

**Pass Criteria:**

- All panel elements present and correctly labelled
- Respond to findings button navigates to AMS screen
- Deadline message shows 8 July 2026 (updated from last year)

